""" Keybindings {{{
    " Useless.
    nnoremap <F1> <Nop>

    " Move around more efficiently
    map d <C-d>
    map s <C-u>
    map j <C-d>
    map k <C-u>

    " Pin tabs easily
    nmap gp :set<Space>apptab<Return>
    nmap gu :set<Space>noapptab<Return>

    " Traditional copy/paste, no matter the mode
    noremap <C-c> <C-v><C-c>
    noremap <C-v> <C-v><C-v>

    " Go to last used tab
    nnoremap gf <C-^>
""" }}}
